itunes:title: I dropped the ball, and it’s time to wise up
title: I dropped the ball, and it’s time to wise up
description:
Been a lazy assed two weeks for me and it’s time to get back on it.

It’s easy to become complacent, it’s also natural, but figuring out when you’ve done that and getting back on it.. is very important to keep making improvements 

Earned and not given

Support the show
